# =============================================================================
# Tajne i okruženja (Preview / Production)
# =============================================================================
# Kopiraj u .env.local (lokalno) ili postavi u hosting dashboardu. Nikad ne commit-uj .env.local.
#
# Rotacija ključeva:
#   • RESEND_API_KEY — rotiraj povremeno i ODMAH posle sumnjivog događaja (Resend → API Keys:
#     revoke stari, kreiraj novi, ažuriraj env u Production pa redeploy; ista procedura za Preview ako ga koristiš).
#   • TURNSTILE_SECRET_KEY / NEXT_PUBLIC_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY — novi par u Cloudflare ako je ključ sumnjiv.
#   • UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN — rotiraj u Upstash ako je token kompromitovan.
#   • SECURITY_AUDIT_SALT — drugačiji nasumičan string po okruženju (lokal / Preview / Production);
#     promena menja ipHash u logovima. Generiši: node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(32).toString('hex'))"
#
# Odvajanje okruženja (npr. Vercel):
#   • Production: posebni secreti za produkcioni domen (Resend, Turnstile za prod URL, salt, opciono poseban Redis).
#   • Preview: posebni ili test ključevi da preview ne šalje mejl na isti inbox / ne koristi prod Turnstile domen ako ne želiš.
#   • Ne koristi production RESEND_API_KEY u PR preview granama ako možeš da izbegneš.
#   • SECURITY_AUDIT_SALT: u Vercel Dashboard → Settings → Environment Variables dodaj istu promenljivu
#     tri puta sa različitim vrednostima: Production, Preview, Development (lokalni `vercel dev` koristi Development).
# =============================================================================

# --- Resend (https://resend.com) — slanje kontakt forme (/api/send) ---
RESEND_API_KEY=re_placeholder_your_key_here
RESEND_TO_EMAIL=office@medensrbija.com
# Verifikovana adresa ili domen u Resend-u (može "Ime <email@domen>").
RESEND_FROM_EMAIL=your-verified-email@resend.dev

# --- Cloudflare Turnstile (opciono; ako je TURNSTILE_SECRET_KEY postavljen, forma mora slati token) ---
NEXT_PUBLIC_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY=your_turnstile_site_key_here
TURNSTILE_SECRET_KEY=your_turnstile_secret_key_here

# --- Security audit (HMAC ipHash u stdout JSON logovima) ---
# Obavezno drugačija vrednost po okruženju. Generiši: node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(32).toString('hex'))"
SECURITY_AUDIT_SALT=your_64_char_hex_here

# --- Upstash Redis — distribuirani rate limit i Resend circuit breaker za /api/send (opciono; bez ovoga = in-memory) ---
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=https://xxxx.upstash.io
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=...

# --- Poverenje zahteva (POST /api/send) ---
# CONTACT_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=https://example.com,https://www.example.com
# TRUST_PROXY_HEADERS=true

# --- Ponašanje /api/send (opciono) ---
# CONTACT_MIN_RESPONSE_MS=320
# RESEND_CIRCUIT_FAILURE_THRESHOLD=3
# RESEND_CIRCUIT_COOLDOWN_MS=90000

# --- CSP (proxy.ts) ---
# CSP_ENFORCE=false
# CSP_REPORT_URI=
